Quickstrike:





"There is somethin' t' talk about!" Quickstrike shouted through his 
comm-link. "An' don't say ya don't! Everytime ya come back t' base, ya come 
back t' base damaged." He knew the incident with Cheetor wasn't her fault. 
He was the one most damaged. But he didn't want to mention that. "Now, me 
an' you need t' talk!"

He knew he was loosing his temper.
